<title>USA: Mylex to buy buy back up to 3.0 mln shrs.</title>
<headline>Mylex to buy buy back up to 3.0 mln shrs.</headline>
<dateline>FREMONT, Calif. 1997-04-22</dateline>
<text>
<p>Mylex Corp said Tuesday its board of directors has authorized a stock repurchase of up to 3,000,000 shares.</p>
<p>The repurchase is about 14.5 percent of the outstanding common shares.</p>
<p>&quot;During the first quarter the company posted a significant increase in cash and short term investments,&quot; said Chief Financial Officer Colleen Gray. &quot;The repurchase program is an excellent opportunity to enhance shareholder value and we believe it represents an efficient use of our cash.&quot;</p>
</text>
